NG0271:0: [(]11[)]@#// blug / yid bzhin gter ldan ka pa lar //
NG0271:1: snying zho sha dang mkhal zho sha / gla gor
NG0271:2: zho sha tsi tra ka / ka ko la sogs
NG0271:3: sbyar ba'i sman // bkra shis mtshan ldan ka pa lar //
NG0271:4: rin chen sna tshogs bdar ba gzhag / khams gsum yongs bsgral ka pa lar //
NG0271:6: tsan+dan smug po li shi dang *//
NG0271:7: skyu ru ra dang star bu dang *//
NG0271:9: mi 'gyur sa mkhregs ka pa lar //
NG0271:10: 'o ma sna tshogs sbyar ba blug / cho 'phrul rtags 'byin ka pa lar //
NG0271:11: bdud rtsi dri chu brag zhun dang *//
NG0271:12: cong zhi dang ni gur gum dang *//
NG0271:13: lce pog dkar po la sogs so //
NG0271:14: mtshan ma spros bral ka pa' lar //
NG0271:15: sna tshogs chu rnams blug par bya //
NG0271:16: ye shes rnam lnga'i ka pa lar //
NG0271:17: dri chen dag dang sbyar ba'i sman //
NG0271:18: dza ti pha la a ru+u ra //
NG0271:19: a ga ru dang du ru ka / gla rtsi dag dang sbyar ba'i sman //
NG0271:20: dri chen dbus la byang sems shar //
NG0271:21: mam sa lho la rak+ta nub //
NG0271:22: dri chu byang ste rtsa ba lnga //
NG0271:23: shar lho chang la lho nub tu //
NG0271:24: rin chen nub byang 'o ma yin //
NG0271:25: byang shar chu ni sna tshogs gzhag / de bzhin dar gyi mthil yol gyis //
NG0271:27: mda' bzhi dang ni dar sna bzhi //
NG0271:28: tshon skud sna lnga phur pa brgyad //
NG0271:29: man+dal de yi rgyan du dgong *//
NG0271:30: rnal 'byor mched dang lcam dral la //
NG0271:31: dza gad phyag tu bzhag nas kyang *//
NG0271:32: las dang bya ba bskos la gdab //
NG0271:33: rang re'i phrin las ci nus bya'o //
NG0271:34: snod rnams sems ma bcu drug bsgom //
NG0271:35: sgeg mo dang ni spos me ma //
NG0271:36: lcags kyu ma dang rdo rje sgrol //
NG0271:37: shar gyi rtsibs la yang dag gnas //
NG0271:38: phreng ba ma dang me tog ma //
NG0271:39: zhags pa ma dang rin chen spyan //
NG0271:40: lho yi rtsibs la yang dag gnas //
NG0271:41: pi wang ma dang mar me ma //
NG0271:42: lcags sgrog ma dang gsal bkra ma //
NG0271:43: nub gyi rtsibs la yang dag gnas //
NG0271:44: gar mkhan ma dang dri chab ma //
NG0271:46: byang gi rtsibs la yang dag gnas //
NG0271:47: bcud rnams sems dpa' bcu drug bsgom //
NG0271:48: der ni tsa ka li yang dgod //
NG0271:49: rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje bsnams //
NG0271:50: rdo rje rgyal po lcags kyu 'dzin //
NG0271:51: rdo rje chags pa mda' gzhu 'gengs //
NG0271:52: rdo rje legs pa se gol sgrol //
NG0271:53: shar gyi rdo rje'i rigs su grags //
NG0271:54: rdo rje rin chen rin po che //
NG0271:55: rdo rje gzi brjid nyi ma bsnams //
NG0271:56: rdo rje rgyal mtshan rin chen tog  / rdo rje bzhad pa so phreng 'dren //
NG0271:57: lho yi rin chen rigs su grags //
NG0271:58: rdo rje chos ni pad+ma bsnams //
NG0271:59: rdo rje rnon po ral gri 'dzin //
NG0271:61: rdo rje smra ba lce yang 'dzin / nub phyogs pad+ma rigs su grags //
NG0271:62: rdo rje las ni rgya gram bsnams //
NG0271:63: rdo rje srung ba go cha 'dzin //
NG0271:64: rdo rje gnod sbyin mche ba 'chang *//
NG0271:65: rdo rje khu tshur khu tshur nyid //
NG0271:66: byang gi sems dpa' las kyi rigs //
NG0271:67: so so'i sku rnams gdod par bya //
NG0271:70: dbus na rnam par snang mdzad che //
NG0271:71: sangs rgyas spyan dang gnyis su med //
NG0271:72: shar na rdo rje mi bskyod pa //
NG0271:73: shar lhor dbyings phyug ma nyid de //
NG0271:74: lho na rin 'byung dkon mchog dpal //
NG0271:75: lho nub ma ma ki zhes bya //
NG0271:76: nub na snang ba mtha' yas la //
NG0271:77: nub byang na bza' dkar mo nyid //
NG0271:78: byang na don yod grub pa la //
NG0271:79: byang shar dam tshig sgrol ma nyid //
NG0271:80: dbus kyi ling tshe dgu po la //
NG0271:81: rigs lnga yab yum sku rnams dgod //
NG0271:82: chos sku dri ma med pa las //
NG0271:83: de bzhin nyid du rnam par gnas //
NG0271:84: longs sku ye shes sgyu ma las //
NG0271:85: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin //
NG0271:86: sprul sku sems can don mdzad phyir //
NG0271:87: rgyu las sangs rgyas sku yang bskyed //
NG0271:89: yul lnga b+ha ga bde ba'i dbyings //
NG0271:90: ma bsgribs yongs su 'od gsal bas //
NG0271:91: gzhal yas khang pa gdan dang bcas //
NG0271:92: bdag 'dzin phung po lnga sogs pa //
NG0271:93: lha sku phyag rgya chen por bsgom //
NG0271:94: 'og min gnas nas spyan drangs nas //
NG0271:95: bzhugs su gsol nas phyag 'tshal te //
NG0271:96: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba dang *//
NG0271:97: de kho na yi mchod pa dbul //
NG0271:98: bstod cing thugs dam bskul byas nas //
NG0271:99: snod kyi 'jig rten gzhal yas khang *//
NG0271:100: bcud kyi 'gro ba lha yi sku //
NG0271:101: 'byung bzhi las skyes rtsi shing dang *//
NG0271:102: nags tshal ma lus snang ba rnams //
NG0271:103: thams cad sman chen ra sa yan //
NG0271:104: dgun gyi dus na rtsa ba'i sman //
NG0271:105: dpyid ni lo ma 'dab mar skyes //
NG0271:106: dbyar ni me tog mdangs dang ldan //
NG0271:107: ston ni 'bras bu smin pa ste //
NG0271:108: snang ba'i dus na stong nyid pas //
NG0271:109: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings su thim //
NG0271:111: bdud rtsi chen po 'khor lo 'bar ba'i rgyud las /
NG0271:112: sman khrol bur bsgrub pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o //
NG0271:113: // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis sman btag btsag
NG0271:114: phye ma sgrub pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0271:115: sbyor sgrol ma mo bcu drug gis //
NG0271:116: btag btsag sbal la sbyar te gzhug / gang zhig sbyor bas sbyang ba ni //
NG0271:117: mar me gso dang tshangs pa'i thog / rtsa dang srub shing thig le dang *//
NG0271:118: gcig gnyis bzhi dang man ngag dgu //
NG0271:119: srin po ru tra k+sha gnas la //
NG0271:120: me rlung drag pos bskyod byas na //
NG0271:121: lte ba'i am yig bdud rtsi 'bab //
NG0271:122: mar me gso bar bya ba'o //
NG0271:123: me rlung rab tu g.yos pa yis //
NG0271:124: spyi bo'i ham yig bdud rtsi 'bebs //
NG0271:125: tshangs pa'i thog ces bya ba nyid //
NG0271:126: dbugs nyid phyir la ldang pa na //
NG0271:127: g.yas kyi ro ma nyi ma me //
NG0271:128: dbugs ni nang du 'jug la ni //
NG0271:129: g.yon gyi rkyang ma zla ba chu //
NG0271:130: rlung nyid khong du gnas pa na //
NG0271:131: dbus kyi kun 'dar ma nyid ni //
NG0271:132: pad+ma chu shing til mar dang *//
NG0271:133: rgya skyegs sdong chen la gnas pa'i //
NG0271:134: phra zhing drang la gsal zhing dmar //
NG0271:135: rtsa yi rnal 'byor bsgom par bya'o //
NG0271:136: dbus ma kun 'dar srog shing la //
NG0271:137: ro rkyang srub thag bsrubs byas pas //
NG0271:141: snying gar nyi zla kha sbyor nas //
NG0271:142: lte ba'i dpa' bo 'ba' zhig la //
NG0271:143: gsang gnas bde ba'i thig le dang *//
NG0271:144: mdzod spu skra dkar sa bon bzhi //
NG0271:145: rlung dang bstun la nyams su blang *//
NG0271:147: bshang sgor rlung la sum mdor me //
NG0271:148: lte ba sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NG0271:149: phyi skor drug cu rtsa bzhi ste //
NG0271:150: nang skor 'dab ma brgyad pa la //
NG0271:151: sde tshan bco brgyad g.yas su bskor //
NG0271:152: lte ba phra ba'i a yig dmar //
NG0271:153: rlung gis me bus a las me //
NG0271:154: rab tu 'bar bar bsgom par bya //
NG0271:156: lte ba dang ni snying ga gnyis //
NG0271:158: thur bstan sngon po hum ni dbus //
NG0271:159: a ham shin tu cha phra bas //
NG0271:161: byang sems dkar dmar rab tu 'dzag / rlung yang rim gyis kha sbyar ba //
NG0271:163: lte ba sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NG0271:164: 'dab ma drug cu rtsa bzhi la //
NG0271:165: a li g.yon bskor ka li g.yas //
NG0271:166: ha dang sha yig rnam par spang *//
NG0271:167: nang bskor sde tshan brgyad kyang dmar //
NG0271:168: snying ga chos kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NG0271:170: phyogs bzhi yab la mtshams bzhi yum //
NG0271:171: dbus na hum yig gnas pa'o //
NG0271:172: mgrin pa longs spyod dkyil 'khor du //
NG0271:173: 'dab ma bcu drug lte ba am //
NG0271:174: yi ge dmar po gyin du lta //
NG0271:175: spyi bo bde chen dkyil 'khor du //
NG0271:176: 'dab ma sum cu rtsa gnyis la //
NG0271:177: a li bcu drug g.yon du bskor //
NG0271:178: ka nas ta sogs bcu drug g.yas //
NG0271:179: ham yig thur bstan yi ge dmar //
NG0271:180: g.yas kyi ro ma'i nang song bas //
NG0271:181: yig 'bru ma lus rnam par bsreg / ham zhu g.yon pa rkyang mar babs //
NG0271:182: rim pas gsal btab lte bar la 'babs //
NG0271:183: 'khor lo bzhi la brten nas bsgom //
NG0271:184: rkang mthil ram las long bu me //
NG0271:185: brla yi rtsa chen gsang gnas 'dzom //
NG0271:186: rno myur drag cing rtsub la tsha //
NG0271:190: thams cad me ru 'bar ba nyid //
NG0271:191: man ngag gnad kyis zin par bya //
NG0271:192: lam sbyangs blta ba rkyang pa dang *//
NG0271:193: drod ni byung rgyal dag tu btang *//
NG0271:194: thun grangs tshad med yod par sbyar //
NG0271:195: yid kyi 'jug yul rab brtags la //
NG0271:196: khams kyi tshad kyang rab tu gzung *//
NG0271:197: yum la sbyor ba byas nas ni //
NG0271:198: rang byung ye shes rnam pa bzhi //
NG0271:199: nyon mongs rnam par rtog pa dang *//
NG0271:200: snel zhi gsal zhing yang ba yis //
NG0271:201: gsang ba'i dbang bskur bya ba dang *//
NG0271:202: sbyar ba'i byang sems sman du blug / sgrol bas sbyang ba bya ba ni //
NG0271:203: ri rab rtse na lha gnas ni //
NG0271:204: yi ge a dkar longs spyod ldan //
NG0271:205: lha min su ni ser po ste //
NG0271:206: 'thab rtsod ri rab khong seng gnas //
NG0271:209: nr-i yig sngon por gnas pa'o //
NG0271:210: phyi yi rgya mtsho dud 'gro gnas //
NG0271:211: du ni dud khar gnas pa'o //
NG0271:212: grong khyer ser skyar yi dwags gnas //
NG0271:213: pri yig dmar po gnas pa nyid //
NG0271:214: rdo rje gdan gyi gdan 'og na //
NG0271:215: dmyal ba tri yig nag por gnas //
NG0271:216: ram yam kham las byung ba yis //
NG0271:217: bkres skom sdug bsngal ram gyis bsreg / glen lkugs yam gyis mtshan nyid med //
NG0271:218: tsha grang kham gyis rnam par bkrus //
NG0271:219: 'bru lnga rigs lnga'i skur gyur nas //
NG0271:220: bsgral nas chos nyid ngang du spar //
NG0271:221: phung po bdud rtsir rab sbyar bya //
NG0271:222: dkar mo dang ni rkun mo dang *//
NG0271:223: rmongs mo dang ni thal byed ma //
NG0271:224: sbos mo dang ni gtum byed dang *//
NG0271:225: sme sha can dang ma tshogs dang *//
NG0271:226: seng stag spyang ki wa mo'i gdong *//
NG0271:227: bzhad dang ka ka bya rog dang *//
NG0271:228: 'ug gdong ma mo bcu drug sbyang *//
NG0271:229: shar du lta ba yangs pas btul //
NG0271:230: lho ru bsgom pa gsal bas btsag / nub tu spyod pa zhib bas sbal //
NG0271:231: byang du 'bras bu mthar phyin sbyar //
NG0271:232: pho mo thod pa kha sbyar nas //
NG0271:233: dar gyis bcings nas bzhugs su gsol //
NG0271:235: bdud rtsi chen po 'khor lo 'bar ba'i rgyud las
NG0271:236: sman phye ma btag btsag gi le'u ste lnga pa'o
NG0271:237: // // de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi bdud rtsi
NG0271:238: gong bu gcig pa'i sman sbyar bar bya ba 'di
NG0271:240: sku dang gsung dang thugs dang ni //
NG0271:241: yon tan phrin las rnam pa lnga //
NG0271:242: stong gsum khro bo sku gdung 'bar //
NG0271:243: rta mgrin dbang dang mkha' mnyam klong *//
NG0271:245: sku yi dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub //
NG0271:246: chos nyid yongs su rgya chad med //
NG0271:247: de phyir lte ba zlum por gnas //
NG0271:248: tshogs brgyad yul las ma rmongs gcod //
NG0271:249: de rtag ka ba mchog brgyad ldan //
NG0271:250: nyon mongs g.yul gcod 'khor lo brgyad //
NG0271:251: yon tan zad med rin po che //
NG0271:252: ye shes bzhi ldan sgo bzhir shar //
NG0271:253: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems //
NG0271:254: mu tig a sma gar+b+ha dang *//
NG0271:255: rin po che yi gdan khri 'bar //
NG0271:256: rigs gsum rigs bzhi rigs lnga nyid //
NG0271:257: rtse gcig rtse lnga rtse dgu grag / nyi zla dbang phyug pho mo dang *//
NG0271:258: byol song gtso bo brgyad steng na //
NG0271:259: rnam par rgyal ba dbyug sngon can //
NG0271:260: gshin rje gshed dang mi g.yo mgon //
NG0271:261: rta mgrin 'dod pa'i rgyal po dang *//
NG0271:262: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa rnam rgyal khams //
NG0271:263: stong gsum khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyis //
NG0271:264: phyogs bcu'i bdud btul mtshamasabacad pa //
NG0271:265: phye ma btags btsag khrol bu dang *//
NG0271:266: gong bu gcig pa kun la khyab //
NG0271:267: shar na bud+d+ha he ru ka / lho na rin chen khrag mthung nyid //
NG0271:268: nub na pad+ma khros pa'i sku //
NG0271:269: byang na las kyi khro rgyal che //
NG0271:270: dbus steng badzra he ru ka / sku gdung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams //
NG0271:271: 'byung lnga'i skal pa rnam sbyang zhing *//
NG0271:272: dug lnga ye shes rnam lnga 'bar //
NG0271:275: me ni gyen 'bar thur du chu //
NG0271:276: rlung ni gsegs la 'gro ba dang *//
NG0271:277: nam mkha' rgyu ba med pas na //
NG0271:278: srog dang rtsol ba'i rang bzhin can //
NG0271:279: rlung lnga la ni yang dag gnas //
NG0271:280: mkha' mnyam klong gi dkyil 'khor ni /
NG0271:281: khro mo gnam zhal dbu dgu+u ma //
NG0271:282: bco brgyad phyag dang yang dag ldan //
NG0271:283: zhabs kyang rnam pa brgyad du gnas //
NG0271:284: lha rnams bskyed dang sbyor ba dang *//
NG0271:285: dbang bskur sbyin sreg la sogs pa //
NG0271:286: yum 'dir rab tu sgrub par byed //
NG0271:287: de phyir mkha' klong rnam par dag / rta mgrin dbang gi dkyil 'khor du //
NG0271:288: rta mgrin gsang ba'i yum dang bcas //
NG0271:289: hum chen stobs chen steng 'og gnas //
NG0271:290: bcom ldan rta yi rgyal po ni //
NG0271:291: mtshams kyi dus na nub na gnas //
NG0271:292: nyu le bzlog na bdag gi sku //
NG0271:293: nam mkha' bar snang gnas la bzhugs //
NG0271:295: bzlas pa dgu yi phyag rgya nyid //
NG0271:296: phye ma gnam zhal b+ha ga na //
NG0271:297: dngos grub zla gam dkyil 'khor steng *//
NG0271:298: dbang bskur las kyi slob dpon nyid //
NG0271:299: khrol bu rus sbal khog pa la //
NG0271:300: mdzad pa'i las yang de bzhin mdzad //
NG0271:302: che mchog ma mo dgongs pa ni //
NG0271:303: dbu dgu phyag kyang bco brgyad gnas //
NG0271:304: che mchog bdud rtsi sman la dgongs //
NG0271:305: phyag na phra men mkha' 'gro dang *//
NG0271:307: che mchog chosanyid dgongs pa ni //
NG0271:308: sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bsnams //
NG0271:309: dbu ni nyi shu rtsa gcig la //
NG0271:310: sangs rgyas bdun gsum nyi shu gcig / phyag kyang bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis so //
NG0271:311: zhabs brgyad rab tu rnam par bzhugs //
NG0271:312: ljags las sa nu he ru ka / dkyil 'khor bdun brtsegs rnam par gsal //
NG0271:314: lus dang ngag dang yid dang gsum //
NG0271:315: sku gsung thugs su rnam par sbyang *//
NG0271:316: 'byung ba lnga yi thugs rje las //
NG0271:317: man+dal brgyad pa'i gzhung bzhin du //
NG0271:318: dpal dang ldan pa'i snod bzhag ste //
NG0271:319: stong las sbyar ba ye nas dag / nyi zla gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NG0271:321: stong khams khyab pa'i don byas nas //
NG0271:322: dus gsum rgyal ba mchod pa'i phyir //
NG0271:323: mu tig dkar po dri med ltar //
NG0271:324: sgrub pa pos ni nan tan bya'o //
NG0271:325: bdag nyid che mchog skur gnas pas //
NG0271:327: ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang ba //
NG0271:328: thugs kar rin chen zur brgyad las //
NG0271:331: thugs nyid 'gro ba'i don la bskul //
NG0271:332: zhe sdang rgyu 'bras rtsad nas bcad //
NG0271:333: slar 'dus bdud rtsi sman la thim //
NG0271:334: mu tig dkar po dri med ltar //
NG0271:335: sgrub pa pos kyang nan tan bya'o //
NG0271:336: bdag nyid che mchog skur 'gyur te //
NG0271:337: ljags kyi pad+ma'i gdan steng du //
NG0271:338: pad+ma sems dpa' tshon gang ba //
NG0271:341: khro bo gsung gi dbyig tu gyur //
NG0271:342: gsung nyid 'gro ba'i don la bskul //
NG0271:344: slar nyid bdud rtsi sman la thim //
NG0271:345: sman nyid bdud rtsi 'od du zhu //
NG0271:347: sgrub pa pos ni nan tan bya //
NG0271:348: bdag nyid che mchog he ru ka / dung khang zla ba'i gdan steng du //
NG0271:349: bde gshegs sems dpa'i tshon gang la //
NG0271:351: sku nyid 'gro ba'i don la bskul //
NG0271:352: gti mug rgyu 'bras rtsad nas bcad //
NG0271:353: slar 'dus bdud rtsi sman la thim //
NG0271:354: sman nyid byang chub sems su zhu //
NG0271:355: btso ma zhi gar brub pa ltar //
NG0271:356: sgrub pa pos ni nan tan bya'o //
NG0271:357: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha /
NG0271:358: 'gro 'dul sku dang sku gdung zhabs su sbyor //
NG0271:359: sku gdung dbu dang mkha' mnyam zhabs su sbyor //
NG0271:360: badzra he ru'i dbu dang b+ha gar sbyor //
NG0271:361: mkha' mnyam dbu dang tshe mchog zhabs su sbyar //
NG0271:362: mkha' mnyam dbus zhal che mchog gsang bar sbyor //
NG0271:363: che mchog phyag dang phyag mtshan zhe gnyis sbyor //
NG0271:364: sa nu ye shes thabs dang shes rab sbyor //
NG0271:365: rta mgrin gsang ba'i yum bzhi gnyis med sbyor //
NG0271:366: sbyor mtshams brgyad na bdud rtsi'i pho brang brgyad //
NG0271:367: sbyor ba brgyad brtsegs nges pa de la rdzogs //
NG0271:368: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha /
NG0271:369: rang byung rtsa ba che mchog gsal ba yi //
NG0271:370: thugs kar nyi dkyil rdo rje 'bru dgu bskor //
NG0271:371: 'phro 'du rang bzhin med la bzlas brjod rlung *//
NG0271:372: gu+u h+ya phyag rgyas bar chad dbang mi gtang *//
NG0271:373: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha /
NG0271:374: bzlas bskul gsung yig bdud rtsi mkha' las bab //
NG0271:375: mkha' nas shangs bra gsang ba'i gsung dang 'dres //
NG0271:376: gsung nyid byang sems dkar dmar gnyis su 'phros //
NG0271:377: rta mgrin sbyor mtshams thams cad dbang du sdud //
NG0271:378: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:379: mtheb srin rta mgrin yab yum sbyor mtshams nas //
NG0271:380: 'od 'phros pho brang rta mgrin yab yum gyi //
NG0271:381: thugs kar phog pas sgal tshigs rta brgyud de //
NG0271:382: byang sems dkar dmar bdud rtsi nyid du gyur //
NG0271:383: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:384: de las 'od 'phros rta mgrin thugs kar thim //
NG0271:385: thugs kyi dbyings su byang sems dkar dmar 'khyil //
NG0271:386: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hri:tha //
NG0271:387: de las 'od zer kha dog lnga ru 'phros //
NG0271:388: sku gdung 'bar ba'i thugs kyi dbyig tu 'khyil //
NG0271:389: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:390: de nas 'od 'dus me long has btab tshul //
NG0271:391: badzra he ru'i thugs kyi dbyig tu 'khyil //
NG0271:392: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:393: de nas 'od dkar srog thag lam mas 'phros //
NG0271:394: dbu yi gtsug tu mkha' mnyam b+ha gar 'khyil //
NG0271:395: om ahhum badzra a mr-ita hum hrihtha //
NG0271:396: de nas 'od zer gyen du thugs nas ljags //
NG0271:397: gsang ba'i lam zhugs thugs kar 'od dmar 'khyil //
NG0271:398: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:401: gtsug gi rta mgrin yab yum thugs kar 'khyil //
NG0271:402: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:403: de nas mar spros pho brang steng du bab //
NG0271:404: rta mgrin sgal brgyud yum mkhar bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NG0271:405: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:406: de 'od gzungs thag rdo rje lu gu rgyud //
NG0271:407: khong seng nas brgyud rnal 'byor thugs bdun rgyas //
NG0271:408: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:409: rang byung brgyud nas gzungs thag brgyud yig 'phros //
NG0271:410: rta mgrin yab yum sbyor ba'i mkha' la 'khyil //
NG0271:411: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:412: de las 'od 'phros sa nu'i mkha' gsang thim //
NG0271:413: sa nu yab yum sbyor mtshams mkha' la 'khyil //
NG0271:414: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:415: de las 'od 'phros thugs las phyag mtshan 'phros //
NG0271:416: phyag dang phyag mtshan sbyor byas slar la 'khyil //
NG0271:417: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:418: de nas mar babs zhabs brgyad dag nas brgyud //
NG0271:419: dbu zhabs sbyor byas byang chub sems su 'khyil //
NG0271:420: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:421: zhabs brgyad byang sems gsang lam zhugs nas ni //
NG0271:422: gsang ba zhabs kyi sbyor byas ljags la 'khyil //
NG0271:423: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:424: de nas mar babs pad+ma'i b+ha gar 'dus //
NG0271:425: smin mtshams b+ha gar sbyor byas dbu la 'khyil //
NG0271:426: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:427: de nas mkha' mnyam zhabs brgyud sku gdung dbu //
NG0271:428: dbu dang zhabs kyi spyod byas dbu la 'khyil //
NG0271:429: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:430: sku gdung so so'i sgal brgyud zhabs la bab //
NG0271:431: ta kr-ita dbu dang sbyor byas thugs kar 'khyil //
NG0271:432: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:433: khro bcu'i 'od 'dus rta mgrin gsang bar zhugs //
NG0271:434: yum gyi mkhar 'phros pho brang bdud rtsir 'khyil //
NG0271:435: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:436: de nas bdag nyid rang byung lha las 'phros //
NG0271:437: sbyor ba brgyad kyis sgrib dag chos skur gsal //
NG0271:438: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:439: bdag nyid bdun brtsegs gsal ba'i che mchog gi / thugs kar 'bru gsum brtsegs par dgu pas bskor //
NG0271:440: lce steng du yang de bzhin gsal ba ni //
NG0271:441: lhums su zhugs pa zhes ni de la bya //
NG0271:442: bzlas pas bskul te ljags steng yig 'bru rnams //
NG0271:443: mgur lam byung nas thugs ka'i 'bru la thim //
NG0271:444: bzlas pas bskul te yi ge phreng ba nyid //
NG0271:445: gzungs thag bskyon pa lhums nas bltams pa'i tshul //
NG0271:446: rtsa ba'i bdun brtsegs che mchog spyi gtsug gi //
NG0271:447: rta mgrin thugs phog dgu pas bskor ba las //
NG0271:448: sbyor mtshams mkha' la 'bru gsal byang sems bstim //
NG0271:449: brgya byin gyis blangs sku khrus gsol ba'i tshul //
NG0271:450: rta mgrin nyid kyi thugs las yig 'bru 'phros //
NG0271:451: che mchog thugs kar rdo rje dgu pas bskor //
NG0271:452: de nas rim rgyud rnam rgyal rigs lnga ste //
NG0271:453: bdun thugs yid gsal gom bdun bor ba'i tshul //
NG0271:455: lnga'i thugs nas dgu pa phyogs bcur 'phros //
NG0271:456: 'khor 'das kun tu til gong bzhin du khyab //
NG0271:457: bzlas pas bskul te 'phags mchod 'gro don byas //
NG0271:458: 'khor 'das yig 'brur gyur pa rol rtsed tshul //
NG0271:459: yig 'bru slar 'dus thugs kar thim gyur te //
NG0271:460: sgal tshig rta brgyud gsang ba'i lam nas byung *//
NG0271:461: rang byung sbyor mtshams byang sems yig 'bru gnyis //
NG0271:462: bdud rtsi byang sems zhu ba khab bzhes tshul //
NG0271:463: de nas gyen du sgal tshigs rta brgyud de //
NG0271:464: thugs kar thim nas yig 'bru 'od du zhu //
NG0271:465: gzungs thag nas brgyud rta mgrin thugs kar zhu //
NG0271:466: rim par che mchog dgyes bstar longs spyod tshul //
NG0271:467: de nas sku gsum yab yum mkha' la 'phros //
NG0271:468: char gyi rgyun bzhin babs pa rab byung tshul //
NG0271:469: snod kyi 'jig rten yum gyi mkha' nang du //
NG0271:470: dug rnams bdud rtsi gyur pas dka' thub tshul //
NG0271:471: de nas slar 'dus phyogs bcu'i khro bo nas //
NG0271:472: bdun brtsegs 'khor bcas bdun brtsegs ngang du zhu //
NG0271:473: 'phro 'dus rang byung rtsa ba gnyi ga la //
NG0271:474: mgal me lta bur bskor ba chos 'khor tshul //
NG0271:475: snod bcud bdud rtsir gyur pas skye shi med //
NG0271:476: dug lnga bdud rtsi gyur pas bdud btul tshul //
NG0271:477: de ltar bdag gzhan don rdzogs bzhi mthar phyin //
NG0271:478: spang blang zhen rtog med pas sangs rgyas tshul //
NG0271:479: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin las lnga //
NG0271:480: sku lnga ye shes sku gdung bgos pa'i tshul //
NG0271:481: om ahhum badzra a mr-i ta hum hrihtha //
NG0271:482: bdud rtsi byang chub sems ni gnyis med chos kyi sku yi tshul //
NG0271:483: byin rlabs bde gshegs longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NG0271:484: sprul sku'i mdzad pa bcu gnyis mthar phyin nas //
NG0271:485: slar 'dus bdud rtsi bum pa'i lung la thim //
NG0271:486: gnyis med bde chen byang chub sems su 'khyil //
NG0271:487: dus gsum bde gshegs gnyis med byang chub sems //
NG0271:488: bdag nyid rang bzhin dkyil 'khor mkha' la thim //
NG0271:489: thabs dang shes rab byang chub sems su 'phros //
NG0271:490: thig le byang chub sems kyi ngang du 'khyil //
NG0271:491: mdzad pa bcu gnyis thig le 'gro don mdzad //
NG0271:492: thugs ni bdud rtsi chen po'i ngang du zhu //
NG0271:493: byang chub sems ni rdo rje sems dpa'i sku //
NG0271:494: me long lta bu'i ye shes dkar la 'khyil //
NG0271:495: dri chen bdud rtsi gser mdog rnam snang mdzad //
NG0271:496: chos kyi dbyings su mngon par sangs rgyas nas //
NG0271:497: sha chen in+d+ra ni la rin chen 'byung *//
NG0271:498: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes chen por gsal //
NG0271:499: pad+ma rak+ta snang ba mtha' yas nyid //
NG0271:500: so sor kun tu rtog pa'i ye shes shar //
NG0271:501: dri chu don yod grub pa ljang gu'i mdog / bya ba grub pa'i ye shes chen po gsal //
NG0271:502: bdud rtsi ye shes chen por rang shar bas //
NG0271:503: snod bcud thams cad dbyings su ye shes shar //
NG0271:504: de las ma gtogs snod bcud gud nas med //
NG0271:505: rtogs pa'i klong na sangs rgyas dgongs pa gsal //
NG0271:507: so'i mkha' la bdud rtsi dbab par bya //
NG0271:508: rus sbal 'gros kyis dbab par bya ba yang *//
NG0271:509: rtsa yi dkyil 'khor nang du dbab par bya //
NG0271:510: lus khams bdud rtsi chen po'i bcud gnas pa //
NG0271:511: sngags kyi yi ges byin gyis rab brlabs nas //
NG0271:512: snying po rlung gis bskul la dbab par bya //
NG0271:513: om ahhum sarba pany+tsa a mr-i ta me pra be sha ya phem phem phem /
NG0271:514: dkyil 'khor rnams su bdud rtsi bskyil ba yang *//
NG0271:515: rtsa nas dkyil 'khor bzhi yi rdzing chen du //
NG0271:516: srog shing gsum gyis bcud la bor byas nas //
NG0271:517: lus khams bdud rtsi chen po gnas su bskyel //
NG0271:518: gsang ba'i sngags kyi byin gyis rab brlabs nas //
NG0271:519: snying po rlung gi gnas su bskyil bar bya //
NG0271:520: srog gi rlung gis nang du rab bskyil te //
NG0271:521: rtsol ba'i rlung gis phyi nas nang du bsdus //
NG0271:522: sa yi rlung gis mig g.yo brtan par 'dzin //
NG0271:523: chu ni zhi gnas bdud rtsi rdzing du 'khyil //
NG0271:524: me yi rlung ni lhag mthong gnas su 'dzin //
NG0271:525: rlung gi rlung ni rdo rje rgya gram brtan //
NG0271:526: yon tan bdud rtsi grub pa'i rtags shar ba //
NG0271:527: byang chub sems kyi 'od ni rdo rje'i rtags //
NG0271:528: dri chen dri ni rnam par snang mdzad la //
NG0271:529: mam sa 'phel ba rin chen 'byung ldan gtso //
NG0271:530: rak+ta'i sgra ni snang ba mtha' yas nyid //
NG0271:531: dri chu'i du ba don yod grub pa'i rtags //
NG0271:532: dam rdzas lnga 'dus lha mo'i gzugs kyang stan //
NG0271:533: 'od ni rnam pa gnyis las grub pa'i sku //
NG0271:534: nyi zla skar ma 'ja' tshon dang *//
NG0271:536: snang ba tsha tsha mar me'i 'od //
NG0271:537: bar chod 'od ni rnam pa gsum du snang *//
NG0271:538: smug nag ma mo skya 'od rgyal po dang *//
NG0271:539: ljang dmar klu gnyan sa bdag 'byung po kun //
NG0271:540: 'od kyi dngos grub bstim nas len thob pa //
NG0271:541: 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob //
NG0271:542: bar chad nyams gyi phyag rgyas rang don sad //
NG0271:543: byung na bsrung zhing bzlog par bya'o //
NG0271:544: dri ni zhim gyur dngos grub rdzas la bsdu //
NG0271:545: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin 'grub par 'gyur //
NG0271:546: bse dri brag srin dri tre tri ti yang bar du gcod //
NG0271:547: sad pa bzhi yi bar chad bsrung bar bya //
NG0271:548: mang du 'phel ba dngos grub tha ma nyid //
NG0271:549: nan tan byas na tshe yi dngos grub 'grub //
NG0271:550: grub pa'i sgra dang bar chad grub sgra gnyis //
NG0271:551: go dang mi go go ba'i sgra dgu 'byung *//
NG0271:552: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang *//
NG0271:553: mngon shes byang sems bdud bzhi 'pham //
NG0271:554: pha rol phrin las phyir mi ldog / dngos grub blangs shes bstim par bya //
NG0271:555: mi go 'byung ba rnga sgra sogs //
NG0271:556: gang yang dngos grub blang ba ni //
NG0271:558: du ba'i rtags ni rnam pa bdun //
NG0271:559: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen dbyibs //
NG0271:560: pad+ma ral gri lcags kyu dang *//
NG0271:561: mchod rten dbyibs 'byung hum gis rdub //
NG0271:563: lha mo lha dang bar chad gzugs //
NG0271:564: bar chad gzugs mdzes dri mi zhim //
NG0271:568: bdud rtsi chen po'i phrin las brtsam pa yang *//
NG0271:569: bar chad bsrung dang ma grub spogs pa dang *//
NG0271:570: dngos grub blang dang dbang rnams bskur ba dang *//
NG0271:571: yon tan 'bras bu las mthar phyin par byed //
NG0271:572: bar chad bdud rnams rab tu bsal ba yang *//
NG0271:573: dang po lam la 'jug pa rnams //
NG0271:574: 'jig rten mi chos bar gcod bsrung *//
NG0271:575: lam la zhugs par gyur pa rnams //
NG0271:576: phyi rol bdud kyi bar chad bsrung *//
NG0271:577: lam drug cung zad brtan gyur na //
NG0271:578: bdud stobs 'phel ba'i bar gcod bsrung *//
NG0271:579: sems brtan lam du gyur pa na //
NG0271:580: ting nge 'dzin gyi bar gcod bsrung *//
NG0271:581: sad pa bzhi yis bsrung bar bya'o //
NG0271:582: nyams kyi sad dang ting 'dzin sad //
NG0271:583: sngags dang lha grub sad pa yis //
NG0271:585: rdzas kyis spo sba dang ting 'dzin sngags //
NG0271:586: rtsal shugs phyung nas 'bad par bya //
NG0271:587: thun mong dngos grub grub chen brgyad //
NG0271:588: mchog gis sku gsum sa la 'gro //
NG0271:589: slob ma'i tshogs rnams ma lus la //
NG0271:590: nus pa'i dbang lnga bskur ba yang *//
NG0271:591: bum pa rdo dril cod pan ming *//
NG0271:592: bdud rtsi bum pa spyir bzhag bskur //
NG0271:593: zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur ba yang *//
NG0271:594: bdud rtsi'i rdzas ni lce la bstim //
NG0271:595: gsang dbang shes rab ye shes dang *//
NG0271:596: bde ba chen po'i man ngag sbyin //
NG0271:598: mkha' 'gro mchod pa'i mthu las byung *//
NG0271:599: phyi mar ting 'dzin sa thob pa //
NG0271:600: drang srong mnyes pa'i mthu las byung *//
NG0271:601: mthar thug sangs rgyas 'bras thob pa //
NG0271:602: sku dang gsung dang thugs dang gsum //
NG0271:604: sangs rgyas mchod pa'i mthu las byung *//
NG0271:605: bdud rtsi chen po'i phrin las mchog / nyan thos rang rgyal byang sems kyis //
NG0271:606: 'bum gyi char yang mi nye bas //
NG0271:607: shin tu brtson pas 'bad par bya'o //
NG0271:608: bdud rtsi chen po'i 'khor lo 'bar ba'i rgyud las /
NG0271:609: bdud rtsi gong bu gcig pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o
NG0271:610: // // de nas rdo rje snying po la sogs
NG0271:611: 'khor rnams kyis bcom ldan 'das la bskor ba byas
NG0271:612: nas brjod pa / bcom ldan 'das ni kun mkhyen mdzod //
NG0271:613: chos sku dri med snying po las //
NG0271:614: gzugs sku gnyis su snang bar mdzod //
NG0271:615: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NG0271:616: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur snang ba //
NG0271:617: shes bya'i dri ma dag par mdzad //
NG0271:618: 'gro drug sems can thams cad la //
NG0271:619: sprul sku'i mdzad pa mthar phyin pas //
NG0271:620: las dang nyon mongs sgrib pa sbyong *//
NG0271:622: sku gsum don ldan che ba'i lha //
NG0271:624: bdud rtsi chen po'i bsgrub pa'i rgyu //
NG0271:625: snod kyi 'jig rten zhing khams su //
NG0271:626: bcud kyi sems can 'khor ba rnams //
NG0271:628: snod las byung ba skyobs pa'i @#//
NG0271:630: bcud las byung ba rtsa ba'i sman //
NG0271:631: bdud rtsi chen po rab 'bar bas //
NG0271:633: bdag cag rnams kyis nges bzung nas //
NG0271:635: zhes rjes su yi rang ngo //
NG0271:636: bdud rtsi chen po 'khor lo 'bar ba'i rgyud las
NG0271:637: yongs su gtad cing bzung nas rjes su yi rang
NG0271:638: bar bstan par bstan pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o //
